    <h1 style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-ansi-language:FR">Instructions aux
        auteurs :<o:p></o:p></span></h1>
    <h2 style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Types de
      contribution<o:p></o:p></h2>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">L&#8217;appel &agrave;
        communications sollicite des
        articles in&eacute;dits, non soumis &agrave; d&#8217;autres conf&eacute;rences ou journaux,
        de l&#8217;un des
        trois types suivants :<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
      text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><span
style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span
          style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><b
        style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
          &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
          FR">Articles centr&eacute;s solutions</span></b><span
        style="font-family:Times;
        mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        mso-ansi-language:FR"> : ces articles pr&eacute;sentent une
        probl&eacute;matique de recherche
        pour laquelle des solutions nouvelles ou des am&eacute;liorations
        significatives de
        solutions existantes sont d&eacute;velopp&eacute;es. Un article de ce type
        devrait inclure
        une validation pr&eacute;liminaire de la solution propos&eacute;e.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:
      inter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><span
style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:
        Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span
            style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><b
        style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
          &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
          FR">Articles d&#8217;&eacute;valuation</span></b><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
        FR"> : ces articles &eacute;valuent des situations probl&eacute;matiques ou
        bien les
        solutions qui ont &eacute;t&eacute; propos&eacute;es au moyen de techniques
        scientifiques telles que
        les &eacute;tudes empiriques, les exp&eacute;riences, les &eacute;tudes de cas, les
        simulations etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
      text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><span
style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span
          style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><b
        style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span
          style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:
          &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times
          New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
          FR">Articles d&#8217;exp&eacute;riences industrielles</span></b><span
        style="font-family:
        Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        mso-ansi-language:FR"> : ces articles pr&eacute;sentent des probl&egrave;mes
        ou des d&eacute;fis rencontr&eacute;s
        en pratique, relatent des cas de succ&egrave;s ou d&#8217;&eacute;chec ou sont des
        rapports
        d&#8217;exp&eacute;rience de pratique industrielle.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span
        style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;
        mso-ansi-language:FR"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;
        mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les soumissions
        sont faites
        dans l&#8217;une des cat&eacute;gories suivantes : <o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"
      style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3"><span
style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span
          style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        Arial;mso-ansi-language:FR">Chercheur, o&ugrave; les crit&egrave;res de
        s&eacute;lection sont
        l&#8217;originalit&eacute;, la qualit&eacute; et la maturit&eacute; de la proposition.
        Cette cat&eacute;gorie
        peut comporter la mention &#8216;industriel&#8217;. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"
      style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3"><span
style="font-size:12.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:FR"><span
          style="mso-list:Ignore">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times
            New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        Arial;mso-ansi-language:FR">Jeune chercheur, pour les articles
        dont tous les
        co-auteurs sont des doctorants. <span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>Lors
        de
        la soumission, ces articles devront &ecirc;tre soumis en cochant la
        case "Jeunes
        chercheurs". Le prix du meilleur article "Jeunes chercheurs"
        pourra &ecirc;tre attribu&eacute; lors du congr&egrave;s.</span><o:p><br>
      </o:p></p>
    <h2 style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Evaluation
      et publication<o:p></o:p></h2>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Tous les
        articles seront &eacute;valu&eacute;s par
        trois lecteurs du comit&eacute; de programme. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles
        s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s seront
        publi&eacute;s dans les actes du congr&egrave;s et feront l&#8217;objet d&#8217;une
        pr&eacute;sentation orale
        lors du congr&egrave;s.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">A l'issue du
        congr&egrave;s, les meilleurs
        articles seront s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s pour un num&eacute;ro sp&eacute;cial soit de la
        revue
        &laquo;Ing&eacute;nierie des Syst&egrave;mes d&#8217;Information, Herm&egrave;s Lavoisier &raquo;, soit
        de la revue &laquo;
        Document Num&eacute;rique, Herm&egrave;s &#8211; Lavoisier &raquo;. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les auteurs
        seront alors invit&eacute;s &agrave;
        r&eacute;diger une version &eacute;tendue de leur article pour la soumettre &agrave;
        un comit&eacute; de
        lecture sp&eacute;cifique.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <h2>Conditions de soumission<o:p></o:p></h2>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles
        sont limit&eacute;s &agrave; 16 pages et
        devront se conformer au mod&egrave;le Hermes-Lavoisier disponible sur
        le site web du
        congr&egrave;s <a class="moz-txt-link-freetext" href="http://inforsid.fr/Biarritz2015/">http://inforsid.fr/Biarritz2015/</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles
        doivent comporter la
        mention d&#8217;un th&egrave;me majeur et &eacute;ventuellement d&#8217;un th&egrave;me mineur
        choisi parmi les
        th&eacute;matiques pr&eacute;d&eacute;finies ou les autres th&eacute;matiques. La langue
        officielle du congr&egrave;s
        est le fran&ccedil;ais. Toutefois le congr&egrave;s est ouvert aux
        contributions de langue
        anglaise. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="font-family:Times;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
        Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
        &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:FR">Les articles
        doivent &ecirc;tre soumis en
        format PDF sur le site <o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"
      style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span
        style="mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New
